data.description: Price reduced for Cash offers only.   Deal fell apart due to Buyer financing.  FHA appraisal complete and came in at $239500. Survey says X zone no flood.   Why RENT when you can buy! Ready to move in to! Make way out to this 2 bedroom and 2 bathroom home located in the Gulf Highlands Community. As you walk up to the home you will notice a nice front porch area. Then make way inside where you will find a spacious layout with laminate floors throughout the living space. The home offers a formal living/dining room space. You will find the kitchen has ways to both the dining room and family room. The family room is a great space to make a TV room or Hobby room. Now make way out to the fully fenced back yard that is perfect for enjoying the beautiful Florida weather. You will find a shed and patio area back there. Make sure to setup an appointment to see this home today! Buyers agent required to schedule physical showing through call center and preview property before submitting an offer.  Please have your agent follow contract submission attachment when submitting all offers. MUST SEE!
